methods.tryGetBytes:
Tries to get the next ByteSlice from the reader.

:param size: (int) - The exact number of chars to place in the slice.
:param bs: (io.deephaven.csv.containers.ByteSlice) - The result, modified in place.
:return: (boolean) true If the next ByteSlice was successfully read; false if the end of input was reached.
